OL,6,FLecturers from Border College have
OL,7,Fbegun their first day of a three-week
OL,8,Fperiod of strikes.
OL,10,FMembers of the EIS (Educational
OL,11,FInstitute of Scotland) and FELA
OL,12,F(Further Education Lecturers
OL,13,FAssociation) are striking in a dispute
OL,14,Frelating to pay.
OL,16,FThis period of strike action is in
OL,17,Faddition to a national day of strikes
OL,18,Fand six days of targeted strike action.
