CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1713406699
OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,F"We should have had this money in our
OL,7,Fpayslips in September 2022. For many
OL,8,FEIS FELA members, the amount of money
OL,9,Ftabled in the second and third years
OL,10,Fof the current offer falls below
OL,11,Fcurrent public sector pay policy.
OL,13,F"The EIS-FELA does not accept that our
OL,14,Fmembers should be treated any
OL,15,Fdifferently to any other public sector
OL,16,Fworkers and are simply seeking a fair
OL,17,Fpay offer which properly reflects the
OL,18,Finvaluable work that we do."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
