OL,3,CLecturers at Border College begin
OL,4,Cthree-week period of strike action
OL,6,F"This is absolutely shameful and
OL,7,Fcompletely contradicts the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment's opposition to
OL,9,FWestminster's anti-trade union laws.
OL,11,F"However, despite these threats, our
OL,12,Fmembers remain absolutely united and
OL,13,Fresolute in our fight to secure a fair
OL,14,Fpay offer for all members."
